mmendations available through the Web Site. We are not responsible for the accuracy, reliability, effectiveness, or correct use of</p><p>information you receive through the Web Site.</p><h2>Your Obligations</h2><p>You agree to: (a) maintain all equipment necessary for your access to and use of the Web Site; (b) maintain the security and confidentiality of your user identification, password and other confidential information relating to your account; (c) provide accurate, true, current and</p><p>complete information about yourself and promptly provide any updates necessary to keep such information accurate, true, current and complete at all times; (d) be responsible for all charges resulting from use of your account, including unauthorized use prior to your notifying us of such use and taking steps to prevent its further occurrence by changing your password; (e) not impersonate another person or entity; (f) not submit, post or transmit any unlawful, infringing, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, defamatory, untrue, vulgar, obscene, profane, hateful, racially, ethnically or otherwise objectionable material of any kind, including, but not limited to, any material which encourages conduct that would constitute a criminal offense, violate the publicity and privacy rights of others, or otherwise violate any applicable local, state, national or international law; (g) not use the Web Site to introduce, transmit or otherwise distribute viruses, worms, time bombs or other computer programming code that is intended to damage, detrimentally interfere with, surreptitiously intercept or expropriate any system, data or information; and (h) not to use the Web Site for chain letters, junk mail, \"spamming\" solicitations (commercial or otherwise) or bulk communications of any kind.</p><h2>Information and Content you Submit</h2><p>Any information, including any content, Personal Information (as that term is defined in the Privacy Policy), copyrightable materials and any other 